channel.title: Uploading Files :: CID guide website
channel.description: To cut a file on the laser cutter, first open up link (wam.wazer.com) There you will need to sign in, get an adult to sign into the website for you. Once you sign in, the workspace will open up automatically Uploading To upload your file click Import File and select your SVG or DXF file Once you have done that, you will see the name of your part, as well as some options
